                     <interp inst="t18261026-123-person814" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. I took up the prisoner, and bring this handkerchief; I found the duplicate of it on his person, and these keys.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18261026-123-person815">
                  JAMES 
                  WILLIAM CRESSY
               <interp inst="t18261026-123-person815" type="surname" value="WILLIAM CRESSY"></interp>
